## ✨ Features

| Category | Details |
|----------|---------|
| 🔍 **URL Scanning** | VirusTotal + Google Safe Browsing + URLScan.io — একসাথে concurrent scan |
| 🤖 **AI Analysis** | OpenAI/OpenRouter দিয়ে automated risk assessment |
| 📸 **Screenshot** | Microlink (fullPage) + thum.io fallback |
| 🧬 **DNS Lookup** | A, MX, NS, TXT records via Google DNS API |
| 📋 **WHOIS** | Registrar, creation/expiry date, country |
| 🖥️ **IP Check** | Reverse DNS + ipinfo.io geo + organization |
| 🔒 **Headers Audit** | HSTS, CSP, X-Frame-Options, X-Content-Type — A–F grade |
| 🐙 **GitHub Review** | AI-powered code security review from raw URLs |
| 🤖 **AI Expert** | যেকোনো cybersecurity question এ answer |
| 🔄 **Auto-Scan** | Group এ link paste করলে automatic scan |
| ⚡ **API Rotation** | Multiple VT/Google/URLScan keys — quota spread |
| 🛑 **Rate Limiting** | Per-user sliding window (5 req/60s) |
| 🧠 **Smart Skip** | Trusted domains (YouTube, Google, etc.) skip হয় |
| 📊 **Risk Scoring** | 0–100% aggregate score with contextual flags |
| 🧵 **Thread Safe** | Locks for Flask threaded mode — race-condition free |
| ✂️ **Message Split** | Auto-splits long reports to fit Telegram's 4096 limit |

---

## 🎮 Commands

```
/start          — Welcome message + command list
/check <url>    — Full multi-engine threat scan
/scan <url>     — Alias for /check
/dns <domain>   — DNS record lookup
/whois <domain> — WHOIS registration info
/ip <address>   — IP reputation & geo check
/headers <url>  — HTTP security headers audit
/github <url>   — AI code security review
/ask <question> — AI cybersecurity expert Q&A
/ping           — Bot latency check
/stats          — Total scans & threats found
/help           — Detailed help menu
```

> 💡 **Group এ যেকোনো link পাঠালে auto-scan হবে — কোনো command লাগবে না!**

