## 🖼️ How It Looks

### Scan Flow
```
User sends link
       ↓
🛡️ CyberGuard Scanning...
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
🔍 Resolving Infrastructure...
🧬 VirusTotal Multi-Engine Scan...
🛰️ Google Safe Browsing Check...
🧪 Sandbox Detonation...
📸 Capturing Screenshot...
🤖 AI Risk Correlation...
📊 Compiling Final Report...
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
       ↓
📸 Screenshot + 📊 Full Report + 🔗 VT Link
```

### Risk Verdicts
| Score | Verdict | Action |
|-------|---------|--------|
| 0–20% | 🟢 **SAFE** | No threats detected |
| 21–59% | 🟡 **SUSPICIOUS** | Use isolated environment |
| 60–100% | 🔴 **HIGH RISK** | Avoid & escalate immediately |

