## 🧠 Smart Features

### Trusted Domain Skip
These domains are never scanned (exact + subdomain match):
```
youtube.com · google.com · github.com · facebook.com
instagram.com · twitter.com · linkedin.com · netflix.com
...and 20+ more
```

### Group-Internal Link Skip
Messaging platform links skip scan automatically:
```
t.me · wa.me · discord.gg · telegram.me ...
```

### Risky TLD Detection
```
.site · .xyz · .top · .online · .club · .tk · .ml · .cf ...
```

### Suspicious Keyword Boost
```
"free-money" · "login-verify" · "account-suspend" · "claim-now" ...
```

### Rate Limiting
- **5 requests per user per 60 seconds**
- Sliding window algorithm
- Auto-cleanup of stale users every 5 minutes

### Message Splitting
Long reports automatically split at:
- Newline boundaries (preferred)
- Code fence boundaries (``` balance check)
- Hard character limit fallback

---

## 🛡️ Security

| Feature | Implementation |
|---------|---------------|
| Webhook Verification | `X-Worker-Secret` header check |
| Rate Limiting | Per-user sliding window |
| Input Validation | Regex-based URL + domain validation |
| TLD Whitelist | Only known TLDs accepted |
| Thread Safety | `threading.Lock` on shared state |
| Memory Safety | Rate dict auto-cleanup |
| File Size Limit | GitHub review capped at 50KB |
| No Persistent Storage | In-memory only, no DB leaks |

